title: <span style="color: #c00000;">**Ebert**</span> appoints <span style="color: #808080;">**Wilhelm Cuno**</span> Chancellor.
subtitle: <span style="color: #c00000;">**Ebert**</span> calls the former <span style="color: #C0A054;">**DVP**</span> member, now <span style="color: #808080;">**independent**</span>, businessman <span style="color: #808080;">**Wilhelm Cuno**</span> to be Chancellor. 
view-if: year == 1922 and month == 11 and wirth_2_failed == 1
max-visits: 1 
tags: event 
new-page: true 
on-arrival: chancellor = 'Cuno'; chancellor_party = 'I'; in_weimar_coalition = 0
face-image: img/ebertcuno.jpg
  
= <span style="color: #808080;">**Cuno**</span> to become Chancellor!

<span style="color: #c00000;">**Ebert**</span> calls the former <span style="color: #C0A054;">**DVP**</span> member, now <span style="color: #808080;">**independent**</span>, businessman <span style="color: #808080;">**Wilhelm Cuno**</span> to be Chancellor. 
<span style="color: #c00000;">**Ebert**</span> has been under fire from our parties <span style="color: #c00000;">**left-wing**</span>, and sometimes the <span style="color: #c00000;">**labour-wing**</span>, due to his collaboration with the bourgeois.

He offers the <span style="color: #c00000;">**SPD**</span> to join his government of experienced businessmen and pragmatic politicians in a broad coalition.

- @join_cuno: The <span style="color: #c00000;">**SPD**</span> joins the Cuno government.
- @tolerate_cuno: The <span style="color: #c00000;">**SPD**</span> tolerates Cuno and his bourgeois cabinet.
- @oppose_cuno: The <span style="color: #c00000;">**SPD**</span> will not work with this government despite the wish of the President.
  
@join_cuno
unavailable-subtitle: Our party is opposed to this, because joining a bourgeois government would reflect badly on us.
subtitle: The left of our party will hate us after this.
on-arrival: spd_in_government = 1; dvp_in_government = 1; z_in_government = 1; ddp_in_government = 1; in_grand_coalition = 1; leverage = 25; foreign_minister = 'Rosenberg'; foreign_minister_party = 'I'; interior_minister = 'Oeser'; interior_minister_party = 'DDP'; justice_minister = 'Heinze'; justice_minister_party = 'DVP'; labor_minister = 'Brauns'; labor_minister_party = 'Z'; reichswehr_minister = 'Geßler'; reichswehr_minister_party = 'DDP'; economic_minister = 'Becker'; economic_minister_party = 'DVP'; finance_minister = 'Hermes'; finance_minister_party = 'Z'; agriculture_minister = 'Luther'; agriculture_minister_party = 'I'; transport_minister = 'Groener'; transport_minister_party = 'I'; postal_minister = 'Stingl'; postal_minister_party = 'BVP'; workers_spd -= 2; left_dissent += 2
choose-if: left_strength <= 20 and reformist_strength >= (left_strength + labor_strength) and early_dvp_cooperation >= 2 and dvp_relation >= 35

The SPD agress to join the Cuno government.

- @selection_of_ministries_cuno

@selection_of_ministries_cuno
title: Select our ministries

We can choose a few ministries. Controlling a ministry allows us to directly effect policy in that area.

- @labor
- @interior_main
- @finance
- @economic
- @justice
- @foreign
- @agriculture
- @reichswehr
- @transport
- @done_cuno
  
@labor
title: Labor Ministry
subtitle: Taking the Labor Ministry is expected of us.
unavailable-subtitle: We do not have enough leverage.
choose-if: leverage >= 5
view-if: labor_minister_party != "SPD"
on-arrival: leverage -= 5; labor_minister_party = "SPD"; labor_minister = "Wissell"
go-to: selection_of_ministries_cuno

Rudolf Wissell of the <span style="color: #c00000;">**SPD**</span> has been appointed labor minister.

@interior_main
title: Interior Ministry
subtitle: Taking the Interior Ministry is expected of us. The Interior Ministry controls domestic security.
unavailable-subtitle: We do not have enough leverage.
choose-if: leverage >= 5
view-if: interior_minister_party != "SPD"

- @appoint_severing
- @appoint_sollmann
- @cancel_interior

@appoint_severing
title: Carl Severing
subtitle: (reformist).
choose-if: leverage >= 5
unavailable-subtitle: We do not have enough leverage.
on-arrival: interior_minister = "Severing"; leverage -= 5; interior_minister_party = "SPD"
go-to: selection_of_ministries_cuno

Carl Severing has been appointed Interior Minister.

@appoint_sollmann
title: Wilhelm Sollmann
subtitle: (non-factional).
choose-if: leverage >= 5
unavailable-subtitle: We do not have enough leverage.
on-arrival: leverage -= 20; interior_minister = "Sollmann"; interior_minister_party = "SPD"
go-to: selection_of_ministries_cuno

Wilhelm Sollmann has been appointed Interior Minister.

@cancel_interior
title: Cancel & Go Back
subtitle: Return without appointing
choose-if: true
