@done_cuno
title: End negotiations

@tolerate_cuno
subtitle: Some in our party think this is a prudent option, after all, why would <span style="color: #c00000;">**Ebert**</span> appoint him if he was a <span style="color: #808080;">**reactionary**</span>?
on-arrival: spd_in_government = 0; dvp_in_government = 1; z_in_government = 1; ddp_in_government = 1; foreign_minister = 'Rosenberg'; foreign_minister_party = 'I'; interior_minister = 'Oeser'; interior_minister_party = 'DDP'; justice_minister = 'Heinze'; justice_minister_party = 'DVP'; labor_minister = 'Brauns'; labor_minister_party = 'Z'; reichswehr_minister = 'Geßler'; reichswehr_minister_party = 'DDP'; economic_minister = 'Becker'; economic_minister_party = 'DVP'; finance_minister = 'Hermes'; finance_minister_party = 'Z'; agriculture_minister = 'Luther'; agriculture_minister_party = 'I'; transport_minister = 'Groener'; transport_minister_party = 'I'; postal_minister = 'Stingl'; postal_minister_party = 'BVP'; spd_toleration = 1; left_dissent += 5 if early_dvp_cooperation == 0

We will tolerate the government. Let's see how this new government is going to play out.

@oppose_cuno
subtitle: We will not betray our ideals for <span style="color: #c00000;">**Ebert**</span>.
on-arrival: spd_in_government = 0; dvp_in_government = 1; z_in_government = 1; ddp_in_government = 1; foreign_minister = 'Rosenberg'; foreign_minister_party = 'I'; interior_minister = 'Oeser'; interior_minister_party = 'DDP'; justice_minister = 'Heinze'; justice_minister_party = 'DVP'; labor_minister = 'Brauns'; labor_minister_party = 'Z'; reichswehr_minister = 'Geßler'; reichswehr_minister_party = 'DDP'; economic_minister = 'Becker'; economic_minister_party = 'DVP'; finance_minister = 'Hermes'; finance_minister_party = 'Z'; agriculture_minister = 'Luther'; agriculture_minister_party = 'I'; transport_minister = 'Groener'; transport_minister_party = 'I'; postal_minister = 'Stingl'; postal_minister_party = 'BVP'; z_relation -= 4; ddp_relation -= 4; dvp_relation -= 3

We will not tolerate the government. The government remains in place for now trying to secure a majority on a issue by issue basis.
